---
// Reusable animated gradient background effect
// Used to reduce duplication of blob animations across pages
---

<div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute top-40 left-10 w-72 h-72 bg-blue-200 dark:bg-blue-900/20 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob"></div>
  <div class="absolute top-40 right-10 w-72 h-72 bg-purple-200 dark:bg-purple-900/20 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-2000"></div>
  <div class="absolute -bottom-8 left-20 w-72 h-72 bg-pink-200 dark:bg-pink-900/20 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl opacity-20 animate-blob animation-delay-4000"></div>
</div>
